{
  "mcpServers": {
    "academic-rag": {
      "command": "uvx",
      "args": ["mcp-academic-rag-server"],
      "env": {
        "OPENAI_API_KEY": "sk-your-actual-api-key-here",
        "DATA_PATH": "~/academic-rag-data",
        "LOG_LEVEL": "INFO"
      }
    }
  }
}

/*
UVX一键安装使用说明:

1. 安装 uvx (如果尚未安装):
   pip install uvx

2. 使用 uvx 安装本项目:
   uvx install git+https://github.com/Jackela/mcp-academic-rag-server

3. 将此配置复制到: %APPDATA%\Claude\claude_desktop_config.json

4. 替换 "sk-your-actual-api-key-here" 为真实的OpenAI API密钥

5. 重启Claude Desktop

优势:
✅ 一键安装，无需本地克隆
✅ 自动依赖管理
✅ 隔离环境，避免冲突
✅ 支持直接从GitHub安装
✅ 自动更新支持

测试连接:
- 在Claude Desktop中发送: "test_connection"
- 或者: "请验证系统状态"
- 或者: "帮我测试MCP连接"

备选配置 (本地开发):
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "academic-rag-dev": {
      "command": "python",
      "args": ["path/to/mcp_server_sdk.py"],
      "cwd": "path/to/project",
      "env": {
        "OPENAI_API_KEY": "sk-your-actual-api-key-here"
      }
    }
  }
}
*/